Modifications by the smoove authors:
  - Import paths rewritten from "@/..." aliases to relative specifiers (with
    explicit ".js" extensions) so the package can be compiled with `tsc` and
    published to npm.
  - Theming is supplied by src/shadcn-bridge.css, which maps shadcn's CSS
    variables onto smoove's design tokens. Component source is otherwise
    unmodified, to keep the vendored copy re-syncable upstream.
  - A small number of `bg-accent` / `text-accent-foreground` usages in the
    vendored tree were repointed to a bridged `surface-hover` token, because
    smoove's `--color-accent` is the hero accent (not shadcn's muted-hover
    surface). See src/shadcn-bridge.css.
  - The vendored tree is excluded from Biome formatting/linting (biome.json)
    so it stays byte-comparable with upstream.
